name: Sultans of the Phoenix-Axe
description: Hailing from the searing apex of Mt. Kalfus, the Sultans of the Phoenix-Axe are renowned for their ability to nullify magic, and travel unseen even amidst extraordinary mages. Now serving as full-time mercenaries (and part-time arsonists), they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
